			<h1>WELCOME</h1>
			<p class="big">Since 2009, Taste of Caribbean Island has been catering to Vancouverites who delight in the exotic and comforting flavours of the West Indies.  From Casual to elegant, Chef Marquise Vilmont prepares the finest organic ingredients combining culinary skill and classic Caribbean Cuisine.  Re-live your favorite paradise dishes. and discover new ones.  We can help you plan your unique event to ensure you and your guests have a wonderful, memorable occasion.  
			</p>

