		<div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="services"> 
		<h1>Catering</h1>
			<p>We specialize in catering with a Caribbean flair.  From casual to formal, you bring the people and we bring the food.  From appetizers and refreshments, to buffets and full multi-course meals, let our food help create the special occasion you will remember... And don’t forget dessert!<p>
			
			
			<h1>Event Planning</h1> 
			<p>No matter what the occasion, we can help create your memorable event. We offer complete party planning, including tents, seating, entertainment, food, and drinks. Planning a Sweet 16 Anniversary or Graduation party? We've got you covered. Elegant or Casual, whatever style you like. Work with our seasoned event designers to plan the perfect event.
			</p>
			
			<h1>Wedding Receptions</h1> 
			<p>	Are you (or someone special) getting married?  We love weddings!  From selecting the venue, to providing dining and bar service, let’s create your special day together.  Our full service Wedding Package includes everything from refreshments and appetizers to multi-course meals... To of course, the cake!
			</p>
			
